Package FizzBuzz.Core

Interface Summary
IRunnable Contract interface for a process which can be Run
ITransformer Contract Interface for ability to transform Integers into strings
IWriter<T> Contract for the capability to write Ts
 

Class Summary
AggregatedTransformer Abstract base class for containers of Transforms
CoalescingTransformer AggregatedTransformer which returns the first of it's children return a non-empty string.
ConcatenatingTransformer AggregatedTransformer which concatenates the outputs of it's children.
EnumerableWriter<T> Runnable process which writes out all of the members of an Enumerable item.
IdentityTransformer Simple Identity Transform.
NullTransformer Transform which always returns an empty string
PredicatedTransformer Implements simple decision making logic in a transform.
Range Represents a range of integers.
Range.RangeEnumerator  
StaticMessageTransformer Transform which always returns a static message.
TransformingTextWriter IIntWriter which transforms the numbers using an ITransformer object before writing them to it's underlying TextWriter.
